  "body": "If you don't mind using another GitHub App for helping with auto merge, I made an open source GitHub App, [Kodiak](https://github.com/chdsbd/kodiak), that supports [auto merging Dependabot PRs based on upgrade type (major, minor, patch)](https://kodiakhq.com/docs/recipes#configuring-automerge-by-upgrade-type).\r\n\r\nIt has a pretty simple config.\r\n```toml\r\n#.kodiak.toml\r\nversion = 1\r\n\r\n# auto merge minor and patch updates made by Dependabot\r\n[merge.automerge_dependencies]\r\nversions = [\"minor\", \"patch\"]\r\nusernames = [\"dependabot\"]\r\n\r\n# let Dependabot update its own PRs\r\n[update]\r\nignored_usernames = [\"dependabot\"]\r\n```",
  "performed_via_github_app": null
}
